<p><span>Zunshine, Lisa. "What to Expect When You Pick Up a Graphic Novel." SubStance 40, no. 1 (2011): 114-34.</span></p>
<p><span>Mickwitz, Nina. “Comics and/as Documentary: the implications of graphic truth-telling. ” Doctoral thesis, University of East Anglia.</span></p>
